==Branch Network==
{{asof|June 2012}}, Bank of Kigali maintained 47 networked branches, in all provinces of the country, making the largest bank in Rwanda, by the size of branch network.<ref>[http://allafrica.com/stories/200905010250.html The Growth of Bank's Branch Network]</ref> The locations of those branches include the following locations:<ref>[http://www.bk.rw/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=139&Itemid=57  Branches of Bank of Kigali]</ref>

