==Directors==
The activities of Bank of Kigali are supervised by a ten-member [[Board of Directors]], all of whom, except one, are non-executive. The current chairman of the board is '''Lado Gurgenidze'''.<ref>[http://bk.rw/english/structure.html The Board of Directors of Bank of Kigali]</ref>

==Management Board==
The day-to-day activities of the bank are administered by a ten-person Management Board, headed by the [[Managing Director]] (MD). The current MD is '''James Gatera''', the only executive director.<ref>[http://bk.rw/english/structure.html Management Team of Bank of Kigali]</ref>

